nd a title page that are provided free of charge. The formatting will be realized according to the standard you specify.</p>','Our Guarantees: 100% Customer Satisfaction | OZessay Writing Service','','publish','closed','closed','','guarantees','','','2017-08-01 17:20:37','2017-08-01 14:20:37','',0,'',0,'page','',0),(202,1,'2012-02-22 15:39:03','2012-02-22 13:39:03','','our-guarantees-v2','','inherit','closed','closed','','our-guarantees-v2','','','2017-08-01 17:20:37','2017-08-01 14:20:37','',201,'https://ozessay-a.akamaihd.net/content/3/en/images/articles/our-guarantees-v2.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpg',0),(203,1,'2012-02-28 14:01:18','2012-02-28 12:01:18','<p style=\"text-align: left;\">&nbsp;Our essay writing service pays particular attention to safety and security of the customers\' data.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\"><img style=\"float: left; margin: 10px;\" title=\"Phoenix Office\" src=\"https://ozessay-a.akamaihd.net/content/3/en/images/articles/our-department.png\" alt=\"Phoenix Office\" width=\"315\" height=\"206\" />Having the professionals experienced in IT security and data safety in our staff, we have been using dedicated servers since 2005. To gain professional strength in the data safety we&rsquo;ve invested much in information security. Today we own 26 physical servers in four data centers in three different countries. All of them are utilized to run websites that we operate, including <a href=\"https://www.ozessay.com.au/\">www.ozessay.com.au</a></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">&nbsp;Be sure that our staff and developers don&rsquo;t have access to customer-sensitive data, such as addresses and credit card information. This information is kept in a separate database with write-only access. It guarantees no hacking attacks and that no personal information will be recovered or disclosed. &nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">&nbsp;How do we treat the customers\' privacy and comfort?</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\