zessay1','','inherit','closed','closed','','college_students_ozessay1','','','2017-05-17 09:03:33','2017-05-17 06:03:33','',225,'https://ozessay-a.akamaihd.net/images/article/og/college_students_ozessay1.jpg?v=1495720068',0,'attachment','image/jpg',0),(227,1,'2012-03-22 22:21:43','2012-03-22 20:21:43','<p style=\"text-align: left;\">Pursuance of a doctoral degree is a lengthy process that requires the candidate to spend heaps of time reading, researching and then writing, writing and rewriting. Working on doctorate degree also means that a lot of technical work that has to be done. Such &lsquo;technical&rsquo; assignments include things like paper editing and proofreading, referencing and formatting etc. If you have reached a PhD level of expertise, it is most likely you can do the research yourself and carry it out at an appropriate level. Nevertheless, our services can still be helpful to you. Among situations our researchers often deal with is helping to carry out raw data analysis, run a background research on the reputable sources of information, look for most current references that are relevant to the topic etc. Those of our writers who work at PhD level can also assist with problems like selecting a thesis, writing a research proposal, editing and rewriting certain parts of your paper as the need may be etc. In other words, from our end we are offering a team of PhD level writers who can provide their peer review with your essay.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">You should also bear in mind that communication between the customer and the writer is beyond simply critical while working on a doctoral level project in Australia. The writer and the customer will be working hand-by-hand; it will not be a mere lead-follow situation, but our researcher will become a research adviser prompting the PhD candidate what the most winning tactics or strategy is. Currently we employ around 150 PhD level research writers who are able to help with a wide variety of topics. We can&rsquo;t state we can complete a PhD level paper on any topic (although we are passionately working towards this direction), so for every new project we will provide a separate response. If you would like to order now, please contact our customer support via email, chat, Skype or the messaging board of your control panel. Looking forward to working with you!</p>','Doctoral Degrees','','publish','closed','closed','','doctoral-degrees','','','2017-05-17 12:31:44','2017-05-17 09:31:44','',0,'',0,'page','',0),(228,1,'2012-03-22 22:21:43','2012-03-22 20:21:43','','doctoral_degrees_ozessay','','inherit','closed','closed','','doctoral_degrees_ozessay','','','2017-05-17 12:31:44','2017-05-17 09:31:44','',227,'https://ozessay-a.akamaihd.net/images/article/og/doctoral_degrees_ozessay.jpg?v=1495701982',0,'attachment','image/jpg',0),(229,1,'2013-11-01 14:00:29','2013-11-01 12:00:29','<p style=\"text-align: left;\">Earning your nursing degree requires tremendous effort and hard work. A nursing specialist becomes a key player in ensuring patient comfort, psychological and emotional well-being. To become such a &lsquo;link&rsquo; a nurse needs to <strong>become a multi-specialist</strong> and be able to liaise with people of various backgrounds, should be knowledgeable in health care, should possess analytical, organizational and management skills. The fact of the matter is &ndash; because of these universal requirements, the nursing degree curriculum often gets &lsquo;littered&rsquo; with other disciplines that seemingly do not have anything to do with their main profession. Nurses are required to run projects like organizational assessments analyze communities, be able to handle risk management problems effectively and so on. Naturally, not all nursing degree students agree that such disciplines are all equally important for a health care specialist.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">Those students, who want to fully concentrate on their health care practice, might benefit from our offers for nursing degree students. In response to the increased demand for <strong>nursing assignments</strong>, we have formed a pool of professional writers who specialize on nursing topics. This group has been quite fruitfully helping our customers to come up with superior nursing papers and pass them in flying colours. For those assignments that are not directly related to nursing per se, we have our team of experienced general writers and researchers, who are proficient in the areas of management, marketing, social studies, creating power point presentations and all sorts of papers that a nursing degree student might request. These services will be able to <em>take the extra pressure off your shoulders</em> and will allow you to focus on areas of your interest in order to master them perfectly. Most of our nursing degree customers are taking this way and we are happy to assist providing the highest possible quality of service.</p>','Nursing Degrees: Become a Multi-Specialist with OZessay','','publish','closed','closed','','nursing-degrees','','','2017-05-17 11:28:34','2017-05-17 08:28:34','',0,'',0,'page','',0),(230,1,'2013-11-01 14:00:29','2013-11-01 12:00:29','','nursing_degrees-v2','','inherit','closed','closed','','nursing_degrees-v2','','','2017-05-17 11:28:34','2017-05-17 08:28:34','',229,'https://ozessay-a.akamaihd.net/content/3/en/images/articles/nursing_degrees-v2.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpg',0),(231,1,'2012-03-22 20:43:57','2012-03-22 18:43:57','<p style=\"text-align: left;\">Writing for international students is our specialty. Many of customers are coming from abroad to earn their academic degrees. In order to meet their needs we have developed a unique program, allowing help them perfect their knowledge and skills. One of the most important things in serving our international students is helping them to get a better command of the language of their study, improve their writing and research skills. To achieve this goal our writers are able to assist international students throughout the writing process, starting from the pre-writing all the way to the post-writing phase.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">Insufficient command of the English language becomes a real barrier for the vast majority of our international students. They might be knowledgeable about the subject, but unable to express their thoughts clearly. Or they might be able to write in English, but an occasional spelling error can occur here and there, or they might be unable to reference their papers accordingly. For every such situation, there is a solution &ndash; our services all cover that. Writers who are working for our company have dozens and hundreds of orders behind their back; this has given them the knowledge and the expertise to become one of the best professionals in the market. Rest assured - if you decided to work with them, your customer experience will become enjoyable, while remaining fruitful and efficient. Try it and you will see why 80% of our customers come back to us to order again!</p>','International Students','','publish','closed','closed','','international-students','','','2017-05-17 11:12:50','2017-05-17 08:12:50','',0,'',0,'page','',0),(232,1,'2012-03-22 20:43:57','2012-03-22 18:43:57','','international_students_ozessay_writing_service','','inherit','closed','closed','','international_students_ozessay_writing_service','','','2017-05-17 11:12:50','2017-05-17 08:12:50','',231,'https://ozessay-a.akamaihd.net/images/article/og/international_students_ozessay_writing_service.jpg?v=1495692184',0,'attachment','image/jpg',0),(233,1,'2012-03-23 21:07:08','2012-03-23 19:07:08','<p>Becoming a <strong>law student</strong>, despite an obvious lawyer glut, is a popular trend that is becoming increasingly palpable worldwide. Despite the high cost and even tougher competition in this market, students keep applying for law schools of all kinds. Obviously, they are drawn by the prestige of the profession, intellectual challenges and financial rewards that are up and waiting for them. Yet, in order to earn a law degree and achieve a high social status, law students need to work ten times harder than any other student. Typical law schools require anywhere from 80 to 90 credits in order to graduate. With some simple calculations, you will see that this equals to about 15 credits per semester, which is quite a load to cope with. Couple that in with the fact that a vast majority of law students needs to work in order to earn their keep as well as pay their loans, the overall workload becomes unthinkable.</p>\r\n<p>If you have found yourself in a similar situation and are looking for help, you have come to the right place. Although <strong>assisting law students</strong> is not as frequent as guiding students who study management or marketing, we do have experienced professionals who can assist you with your assignment and guide you through the process. To ensure maximum efficiency of writing, we typically try to find a writer who specializes in a very specific and narrow area of law. In some cases, the requested writer might be unavailable, in which case we will do a brief research in our database to determine whether we are able to assist. Therefore the best recommendation for law students would be to contact staff prior to placing your order and they will assist you with locating a person with the most suitable background.</p>\r\n<p>The list of our services does not necessarily limit to writing on legal topics. If you are a <strong>law student</strong> but have taken a secondary course which you want to just pass, our company would be an excellent solution! In this case, all you have to do is visit our order page and fill out the form. You will then be receiving instructions on how to work with your control panel and communicate with your writer directly. If you have any questions that need additional clarification, feel free to contact our customer support via email, phone, chat, Skype or via the messaging board of your control panel and you will get a response within no later than 24 hours from the time of your initial inquiry.</p>','Law Degree','','publish','closed','closed','','law-degree','','','2017-05-23 15:47:04','2017-05-23 12:47:04','',0,'',0,'page','',0),(234,1,'2012-03-23 21:07:08','2012-03-23 19:07:08','','law_degree_ozessay','','inherit','closed','closed','','law_degree_ozessay','','','2017-05-23 15:47:04','2017-05-23 12:47:04','',233,'https://ozessay-a.akamaihd.net/images/article/og/law_degree_ozessay.jpg?v=1495543612',0,'attachment','image/jpg',0),(235,1,'2013-11-01 13:27:17','2013-11-01 11:27:17','<p>Book authors can use the services we provide by contacting our company\'s professional researchers to work on their respective books. Our services can be useful whenever book writing process goes into a stall by needing research or statistical calculations or some background research. Whatever the case, we can effectively provide you with the quality service. We understand that writing a fiction book may not always be easy to catch for a ghost writer.</p>\r\n<p>However, we do understand that some books may require purely technical writing, research, proper structurization, proofreading, searching for background information etc. Should this be the case, we are the right company for book authors to give the writing to. Our writers are able to catch your unique style of writing and will imitate it consistently throughout the paper so that the style retains its homogeneity throughout the book.</p>\r\n<p>One of the strongest aspects of our writing service is that it employs a number of Australian books authors with various backgrounds. This means that our company has got all the resources to meet the most specific requirements that our customers set. Our writing professionals are capable of carrying out the necessary research and writing at all possible levels of complexity.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>One of the convenient options we offer our customers is step-by-step working on the project. If you are hesitant to start, you will have the advantage of starting to work in small steps to make sure the assigned writing professionally is exactly the right person to work with you.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Besides that, the works of our Australian books authors are also protected with our customer satisfaction guarantee, including the 60-day money back warranty, a free plagiarism scan, and a 20-day revision opportunity.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Additionally, our support staff is always here for you and ready to assist. We will be happy to do some book writing for you!</p>','Help to Book Authors: The Lost Inspiration Can Be Found at OZessay','','publish','closed','closed','','book-authors','','','2017-05-16 13:59:25','2017-05-16 10:59:25','',0,'',0,'page','',0),(236,1,'2013-11-01 13:27:17','2013-11-01 11:27:17','','book-authors3-v3','','inherit','closed','closed','','book-authors3-v3','','','2017-05-16 13:59:25','2017-05-16 10:59:25','',235,'https://ozessay-a.akamaihd.net/content/3/en/images/articles/book-authors3-v3.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpg',0),(237,1,'2013-11-01 13:30:07','2013-11-01 11:30:07','<h2 style=\"text-align: left;\">How Do We Detect Plagiarism?</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">Our plagiarism detection module is an unalienable part of the website and the services we provide. This module allows us to provide only original papers, as we have a zero tolerance policy towards plagiarism. We also take immense pride in showing the actual report to our customers. This means that all our customers without exception have the privilege of not simply looking at the similarity index (this is another name for plagiarism score), but also have the ability to view the entire report. In case you see that a certain part of your paper shows a similarity index that is too high we recommend that you message your writer directly and ask him/her to explain this score. Very often it happens that if the paper is high in citations, it will show a higher similarity index than a regular paper. This is especially the case with legal papers, where a lot of quotations and references to the active legislation need to be made. The machine checker is simply looking for matches while running a search of its own, and it shows any matches as plagiarism. Therefore, in this case, the final say is to be made by the support staff &ndash; after they review the paper they will be able to determine whether the paper needs to be redone or not. However, if you need a&nbsp;<strong style=\"font-family: verdana, geneva;\"><a class=\"wicon\" style=\"text-decoration: none;\" title=\"When you\'re not satisfied with the paper\" href=\"../../if-you-are-not-satisfied-with-the-paper\">revision</a></strong> you can request it by clicking on the &ldquo;Request a free revision&rdquo; link of your control panel. Once you click on it, a new window will appear, asking you for instructions. Simply fill it in &ndash; and you are all set, the writer will then be alerted to revise the paper. If revisions don&rsquo;t help and you want to change your writer, let us know and our staff will review the case and do a quick reassign.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">Our anti-plagiarism module was been <strong>launched in 2007</strong> and serves us today. We continue to work on improving its accuracy to achieve the best possible results. Therefore, we are checking all papers not only against the text that is available online but also run a brief scan through our database of papers. This helps us to ensure that all papers are <strong>truly authentic</strong> and are not similar to the works completed in the past.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">Our module works in the following manner: it is separating the text into small blocks, called patterns. Then the system performs a web search by utilizing a so-called \"Rabin-Karp\" algorithm of string text search, thus giving the most precise results, (it even includes sources where the parts of the paper were copied from). This technology was invented back in 1987, and we found it to be an adequate solution for our clients\' needs. The system is powered by such search engines as Yahoo!, Google, MSN.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">It has already been mentioned that the system is unable to tell whether a match is an instance of plagiarism or a quotation. Because of this, whenever the paper&rsquo;s similarity index goes beyond 20%, it should be reviewed manually. If the highlighted phrase contains a reference of the original work, then this can&rsquo;t be considered plagiarism. If, however, the phrase does not indicate the original author, this means the paper requires immediate attention. Such papers are reviewed by our team and analyzed for authenticity in a manual mode.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\"><strong><a style=\"text-decoration: none;\" title=\"Place an Order\" href=\"https://www.ozessay.com.au/order\">CLICK HERE TO PLACE YOUR ORDER!</a></strong></p>','Plagiarism Check','','publish','closed','closed','','plagiarism-check','','','2017-05-16 16:03:40','2017-05-16 13:03:40','',0,'',0,'page','',0),(238,1,'2013-11-01 13:30:07','2013-11-01 11:30:07','','plagiarism-check2-v1','','inherit','closed','closed','','plagiarism-check2-v1','','','2017-05-16 16:03:40','2017-05-16 13:03:40','',237,'https://ozessay-a.akamaihd.net/content/3/en/images/articles/plagiarism-check2-v1.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpg',0),(239,1,'2012-03-23 20:59:13','2012-03-23 18:59:13','<p>Many people have a natural talent for writing but have no place to use it after their academic career is concluded. If this describes you, consider becoming a freelance writer with our expert writing team at <strong><em>OZessay</em></strong>!&nbsp;A writing career with <strong><em>OZessay</em></strong> provides you with the ability to use your natural writing ability and specialized knowledge in certain areas, and get paid for every word you write. Become a professional writer today, and realize the benefits of a rewarding career helping other people with their writing assignments.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">How to Become a Writer</h2>\r\n<p>Becoming a freelance writer is as simple as contacting <strong><em>OZessays</em></strong> and filling out a simple application form. We\'ll review your personal profile, and verify that you\'ll be a good fit moving forward as a qualified, professional writer.&nbsp;From this point on you\'ll enjoy all the benefits of a writing career with <strong><em>OZessays</em></strong>, having access to many of the hundreds of new orders that come in each week.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Writing Requirements</h2>\r\n<p>At <strong><em>OZessays</em></strong>, we have high standards for the types of writers we employ, in order to ensure a top notch result for our clients. At the minimum, we require that you be dependable; that means you\'ll need to be available by phone and via email so that our customers can have access to you to discuss their orders with high frequency.&nbsp;Secondly, we require our top-notch team of writers to have polished writing skills. Luckily, if this call for talent sparked your interest, this likely already applies to you. Become a professional writer not only to demonstrate your perfect spelling, punctuation, and grammar but also to polish it. We also ask that our writers have significant experience, whether this means prior work for another writing service, or hours of experience writing a specific type of paper.&nbsp;Last, our writers need to have some expertise in one or more issue areas, and the ability to research. We have Ph.D. candidates and experts in their fields among our talented staff; this wealth of knowledgeable writers allows us to create the well-researched work that our clients have come to expect from <em><strong>OZessays.</strong></em>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">The Advantages of a Writing Career</h2>\r\n<p>There are various advantages to becoming a freelance writer with <strong><em>OZessays</em></strong>. We offer a regular, in time and the competitive salary that meets the needs of our writing talent so that you can focus on satisfying the customer.&nbsp;We also allow a flexible schedule, so that your life doesn\'t revolve around your work for <em><strong>OZessays</strong></em>, despite the customers\' perception that you\'re with them at every step of the writing process.&nbsp;Does all this sound like the right career for you? Become a professional writer for <strong><em>OZessays</em></strong> today and discover the world of exercising your writing ability for an income.</p>','Writing Career: How to Become a Member of the Writing Team at OZessay?','','publish','closed','closed','','writing-career','','','2017-05-16 13:19:54','2017-05-16 10:19:54','',0,'',0,'page','',0),(240,1,'2012-03-23 20:59:13','2012-03-23 18:59:13','','writing-career-v6','','inherit','closed','closed','','writing-career-v6','','','2017-05-16 13:19:54','2017-05-16 10:19:54','',239,'https://ozessay-a.akamaihd.net/content/3/en/images/articles/writing-career-v6.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpg',0),(241,1,'2014-02-06 11:11:37','2014-02-06 09:11:37','<p style=\"text-align: left;\">Insight Innovations LLC is an international company with a headquarters in Scottsdale, AZ. The company is currently working on the US, UK and Australian market and has its respective affiliates in these countries. Such branching has been introduced because we want to assist our customers as effectively as possible; this mode of operation allows us to fully meet our customers&rsquo; needs by working in the same time zone with our customers.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">Ozessay.com.au is an Australian affiliate of Insight Innovations LLC.</p>\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: center;\">The address of our head office is:</h3>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">12601 N Cave Creek Rd<br />Ste #111<br /> Phoenix, AZ 85022</p>','Our Offices: OZessay - an International Company Since 2005','','publish','closed','closed','','our-offices','','','2017-05-17 11:13:23','2017-05-17 08:13:23','',0,'',0,'page','',0),(242,1,'2014-02-06 11:11:37','2014-02-06 09:11:37','','','','inherit','closed','closed','','','','','2017-05-17 11:13:23','2017-05-17 08:13:23','',241,'',0,'attachment','image/',0),(243,1,'2012-03-20 16:27:51','2012-03-20 14:27:51','<p style=\"text-align: left;\">Communication with your writer is the key to the overall project success. Make sure you provide all the necessary instructions.</p>\r\n<hr />\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><a href=\"https://www.ozessay.com.au/ideas-for-successful-collaboration\">IDEAS FOR SUCCESSFUL COLLABORATION</a></strong></p>\r\n<hr />\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: left;\">How Can You Reach the Staff?</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">Means of communication include phone, email, Skype, chat and the communication panel of your customer dashboard. Feel free to use whichever is the most convenient for you.</p>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: left;\">How Can You Reach Your Writer?</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">If you want to contact your writer, use the message board which is located in your personal <a title=\"Control Panel Dashboard\" href=\"https://www.ozessay.com.au/control-panel\">control panel</a>. Here is what you need to do:</p>\r\n<ul style=\"text-align: left;\">\r\n<li style=\"text-align: left;\"><em>Log into your control panel and then click on the order you want to talk to your writer about.</em></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<hr />\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\"><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://ozessay-a.akamaihd.net/content/3/en/images/articles/click-on-the-order-number-to-write-a-message.jpg\" alt=\"Click on the order number to go to the messages block\" width=\"750\" height=\"171\" /></p>\r\n<hr />\r\n<ul style=\"text-align: left;\">\r\n<li style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;<em>After clicking on the order you want, navigate to the button that says \"Write a Message\".&nbsp;</em></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<hr />\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\"><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://ozessay-a.akamaihd.net/content/3/en/images/articles/messages-block-with-a-write-a-message-button.jpg\" alt=\"Write a message button\" width=\"750\" height=\"64\" /></p>\r\n<hr />\r\n<ul style=\"text-align: left;\">\r\n<li style=\"text-align: justify;\"><em>You can write either directly to the writer, or a member of our support staff who will be happy to pass a message to your writer. So chose the receiver of your message in the drop-down list, type your request and hit \"Send\".&nbsp;</em></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<hr />\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\"><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://ozessay-a.akamaihd.net/content/3/en/images/articles/write-a-new-message-either-to-your-writer-or-the-staff.jpg\" alt=\"Write a new message either to your writer or to the staff\" width=\"750\" height=\"204\" /></p>\r\n<hr />\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">We strongly encourage you to communicate with your writer as much as possible, especially during the pre-writing stage. 90% problems can be avoided by simply asking questions and communicating with your writer.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">Please do not reveal any personal information such as your name, address or banking information in any of your messages. We take privacy protection very seriously but it\'s up to you to make sure you don\'t directly give personal information to a third party.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">We truly hope you find this experience enjoyable and take advantage of the direct messaging panel. Remember, whenever you need help, additional assistance or a process update, let us know and <a title=\"Place an Order\" href=\"https://www.ozessay.com.au/order\">we will do our best to assist you</a>.</p>','How to Communicate with Your Writer or Ways to Stay in Touch with OZessay','','publish','closed','closed','','how-to-communicate-with-your-writer','','','2017-05-16 13:55:07','2017-05-16 10:55:07','',0,'',0,'page','',0),(244,1,'2012-03-20 16:27:51','2012-03-20 14:27:51','','communication-with-your-writer-oz-v3','','inherit','closed','closed','','communication-with-your-writer-oz-v3','','','2017-05-16 13:55:07','2017-05-16 10:55:07','',243,'https://ozessay-a.akamaihd.net/content/3/en/images/articles/communication-with-your-writer-oz-v3.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpg',0),(245,1,'2012-03-20 17:37:52','2012-03-20 15:37:52','<p>Assignments that are set up well at the beginning tend to be the most successful. Our studies show that most <strong>problems occur</strong> because of <strong>incomplete or poorly worded instructions</strong>. Our writers are very talented but they aren\'t exactly mind-readers. It\'s better to be overly specific with your requirements instead of assuming the writer will know exactly what research you need them to do. It\'s always a good idea to confirm with the writer before they start writing that they are confident they know what you need. That way you can clear up any confusion before it impacts the assignment.</p>\r\n<hr />\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;<strong><a href=\"https://www.ozessay.com.au/how-to-get-good-grades\">HOW TO GET GOOD GRADES?</a><br /></strong></p>\r\n<hr />\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">Be prepared to routinely <a title=\"How to Communicate with Your Writer\" href=\"https://www.ozessay.com.au/how-to-communicate-with-your-writer\">follow up with the writer</a> as they work on your assignment. Don\'t expect the writer to do all the work for you. Our services are not for cheating in your classes. Rather, they are meant to help you learn and understand your topic. Like a video game walkthrough, our writers are there to help you navigate especially hard levels with instructions and guidance. They aren\'t going to play the game for you. So make sure you understand what the writer is developing for you and reach out to them immediately if you find something is confusing or unclear.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\"><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://zipstudy-a.akamaihd.net/images/articles/big-three-a-key-to-your-successful-paper.png\" alt=\"Big Three: You, Writer and Support\" width=\"650\" height=\"325\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">Responding promptly to your writer\'s questions is <strong>another key to successful collaboration</strong>. When a writer has a question for you try to get back to them as soon as you see their message. The same goes for staff. If you bring an issue to us, try to maintain open, timely communication while we work to fix the problem.</p>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: left;\">Here is a short summary of quick and dirty tips:</h2>\r\n<ul style=\"text-align: left;\">\r\n<li style=\"text-align: justify;\"><em>Be precise about what you want, prepare your assignment description;</em></li>\r\n<li style=\"text-align: justify;\"><em>Maintain contact with your writer at all times;</em></li>\r\n<li style=\"text-align: justify;\"><em>Do let us know in case your writer is not responding do your messages;&nbsp;</em></li>\r\n<li style=\"text-align: justify;\"><em>Keep track of the order progress as your paper is being written;</em></li>\r\n<li style=\"text-align: justify;\"><em>Ask for drafts of your paper so that you can make sure your paper is on the right track.</em></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">We will always prosecute unprofessional or unsatisfactory behavior from our writers. However, this process will not fix a missed deadline or a ruined grade for you. So taking steps to prevent problems from arising will benefit you in the long run.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">Immediately <strong>let a staff member know if your writer is not responsive</strong>, does not provide a rough draft after committing to the project, or is in any other way showing signs that they don\'t intend to <a title=\"Place an Order\" href=\"https://www.ozessay.com.au/order\">complete your assignment</a>. Our staff can smooth out misunderstandings or assign you a new writer if needed.</p>','Ideas for Successful Collaboration: Get the Most of OZessay Services','','publish','closed','closed','','ideas-for-successful-collaboration','','','2017-05-16 13:38:36','2017-05-16 10:38:36','',0,'',0,'page','',0),(246,1,'2012-03-20 17:37:52','2012-03-20 15:37:52','','ideas_for-successful-collaboration-oz-v2','','inherit','closed','closed','','ideas_for-successful-collaboration-oz-v2','','','2017-05-16 13:38:36','2017-05-16 10:38:36','',245,'https://ozessay-a.akamaihd.net/content/3/en/images/articles/ideas_for-successful-collaboration-oz-v2.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpg',0),(247,1,'2012-03-20 18:07:13','2012-03-20 16:07:13','<p style=\"text-align: left;\">Your control panel is a powerful tool allowing you to keep track of everything that is going on with all your orders. We believe your customized <a title=\"Control Panel\" href=\"https://www.ozessay.com.au/control-panel\">control panel</a> contains all the features you need for effective control over the writing process. Let&rsquo;s explain it in greater details.</p>\r\n<hr />\r\n<h4 style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><a href=\"https://www.ozessay.com.au/if-you-are-not-satisfied-with-the-paper\">IF YOU ARE NOT SATISFIED WITH YOUR PAPER</a></strong></h4>\r\n<hr />\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">Once you have placed an order, an email will be sent to you containing your login and your password to the control panel. You will be able to change your password for greater security and convenience.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">Once you\'re logged into your control panel you\'ll be able to see a table that lists all your orders. Here is what the list looks like:</p>\r\n<hr />\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\"><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://ozessay-a.akamaihd.net/content/3/en/images/articles/my-orders-list-on-the-personal-dashboard-ozessay.jpg\" alt=\"Order list on the personal dashboard\" width=\"750\" height=\"173\" /></p>\r\n<hr />\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">The upper section will show you an overview of your account, including your region, account balance, total amounts of the orders made, and your discount level.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">The table right below has several columns that contain important information regarding your order. The date the order was placed will be listed under the \"<strong>Date</strong>\" column. The \"<strong>Deadline</strong>\" column shows the deadline for the orders in progress, and only with late orders displayed in red. The paper\'s progress is shown under the \"<strong>Progress</strong>\" column. You can find the writer\'s ID in the \"<strong>Writer</strong>\" column where you have the option to sort your orders by ID. &nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">If you have more than 8 orders they will be organized into separate pages so make sure to click through them all.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">When you click on your order you\'ll be taken to a page where you\'ll be able to upload additional instructions or directly <a title=\"How to Communicate with Your Writer\" href=\"https://www.ozessay.com.au/how-to-communicate-with-your-writer\">communicate with the writer or staff</a>.</p>\r\n<hr />\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\"><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://ozessay-a.akamaihd.net/content/3/en/images/articles/how-to-attach-a-file-with-instructions.jpg\" alt=\"Attach a file with instructions\" width=\"750\" height=\"193\" /></p>\r\n<hr />\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">You can also contact the writer or a member of our staff by clicking on \"One Touch Support Request\", which is located beneath your orders table.</p>','Tips for Using the Control Panel','','publish','closed','closed','','tips-for-using-the-control-panel','','','2017-05-17 10:40:53','2017-05-17 07:40:53','',0,'',0,'page','',0),(248,1,'2012-03-20 18:07:13','2012-03-20 16:07:13','','control-panel-usage-tips-oz-v2','','inherit','closed','closed','','control-panel-usage-tips-oz-v2','','','2017-05-17 10:40:53','2017-05-17 07:40:53','',247,'https://ozessay-a.akamaihd.net/content/3/en/images/articles/control-panel-usage-tips-oz-v2.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpg',0),(249,1,'2012-03-20 18:34:32','2012-03-20 16:34:32','<p style=\"text-align: left;\">You have the option to request a revision of your order if you aren\'t satisfied with it. Simply click the \"Request a Free Revision\". A pop-up will appear prompting you to provide instructions for the revision. Please be as detailed and precise as possible so your writer can satisfactorily fulfill your request.</p>\r\n<hr />\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><a href=\"https://www.ozessay.com.au/how-to-communicate-with-your-writer\">HOW TO COMMUNICATE WITH YOUR WRITER</a></strong></p>\r\n<hr />\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">The best way to give instructions is to list the problems point by point and explain exactly how you want your writer to fix them. If you need any help communicating what revisions you need please reach out to a member of our staff.</p>\r\n<hr />\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\"><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://ozessay-a.akamaihd.net/content/3/en/images/articles/if-you-are-not-satisfied-with-the-ordered-paper-ozessay.jpg\" alt=\"Request a free revision, if you are not satisfied with your paper\" width=\"750\" height=\"204\" /></p>\r\n<hr />\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">You are entitled to an unlimited number of revisions within a 20 day period. The writer is instantly alert via email when you request a revision. If your revision is especially urgent you can send a message to one of our support representatives who will contact the writer to make sure they start working right away.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">We\'ve discovered that the need for revisions is almost always because of inaccurate or unclear assignment instructions. If you make sure to provide clear instructions when you first <a title=\"Place an Order\" href=\"https://www.ozessay.com.au/order\">set up an order</a> you can save your and your writer\'s time and effort.</p>','What to Do if You Are Not Satisfied with Your Paper from OZessay?','','publish','closed','closed','','if-you-are-not-satisfied-with-the-paper','','','2017-05-13 14:32:50','2017-05-13 11:32:50','',0,'',0,'page','',0),(250,1,'2012-03-20 18:34:32','2012-03-20 16:34:32','','if-you\'re-not-satisfied-with-the-paper-you-ordered-oz-v2','','inherit','closed','closed','','if-you\'re-not-satisfied-with-the-paper-you-ordered-oz-v2','','','2017-05-13 14:32:50','2017-05-13 11:32:50','',249,'https://ozessay-a.akamaihd.net/content/3/en/images/articles/if-you\'re-not-satisfied-with-the-paper-you-ordered-oz-v2.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpg',0),(251,1,'2012-03-20 19:15:13','2012-03-20 17:15:13','<h1 style=\"text-align: left;\">5 Tips for Boosting Your Grades</h1>\r\n<p id=\"content_body\" style=\"text-align: left;\">Getting good grades in school isn\'t something that just happens. It takes persistence, patience and a lot of effort on your part. Going from getting mediocre grades into good grades isn\'t going to happen overnight. It takes time to get yourself organized and develop the skills you need to succeed. To help you boost your grades, here are a few simple tips you can start implementing today.</p>\r\n<hr />\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><a href=\"https://www.ozessay.com.au/tips-for-using-the-control-panel\">TIPS FOR USING THE CONTROL PANEL</a></strong></p>\r\n<hr />\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: left;\">1. Attendance Isn\'t Optional</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">You can\'t expect to learn anything if you aren\'t actually in the classroom to take in the information being taught. Being present in the classroom is crucial to improving your grades. By just listening to what the teacher has to say, you stand a chance of being able to walk away with at least a C. When you take notes and study further about the subject matter at hand, you are going to boost your grade even further. The skipping class will cause you to lose points and make your grade suffer further.</p>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: left;\">2. Keep Distractions to a Minimum</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">If there is anything around you that could be a distraction and prevent you from learning, you need to get rid of it. Don\'t play around with your phone, listen to music or sit so far back in the classroom that you can\'t see or hear what the teacher is talking about. Sit closer to the front of the room to make sure you can hear what the teacher is saying and take accurate notes. Don\'t allow other classmates who might not be interested in learning to distract you from bettering yourself.</p>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: left;\">3. Pay Attention to Your Note-Taking</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">Whatever the teacher talks about in class, you can plan on it being on the exam. Because of this, you need to make sure you are taking accurate notes that you can study from before the exam. Most of the time, teachers discuss the things that they feel are the most important. With accurate notes, you should have no problem passing the test. Go over everything the teacher discussed and make sure you know the material inside and out. Make note cards, discuss the material with the teacher or a friend, do whatever it takes to come out ahead and make sure the material is embedded in your brain.</p>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: left;\">4. Read through Your Textbooks</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">Regardless of how much your teacher might try to fit everything into their class session, it isn\'t going to happen. They only have so much time to go over all of the material. Because of this, you have to take it upon yourself to go through the textbook provided and do your own research and studying. For many students, the thought of reading through pages upon pages of text can be intimidating and overwhelming. This is where you need to implement techniques like scanning, skimming and spotting keywords.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\"><strong>Skimming</strong> involves going through and reading just the most important parts of the content. Reading the first sentence of every paragraph can help you pick up what the text is about quickly.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\"><strong>Scanning</strong> is where you look through the main parts in a book to figure out whether it relates to your given topic. By reading the preface, index, intro and conclusion, you can get a good idea whether the book is going to help you or not.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\"><strong>Spotting keywords</strong> involve going through and picking out the important phrases or words within the text. Anything highlight in italics or bold tends to be the most significant piece of information in the text. Pay attention for this formatting when reading the text.</p>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: left;\">5. Compare Your Notes with the Textbooks</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">The key to mastering the material at hand is reading, analyzing and memorizing the materials. Read through your notes, write down any questions you might have and ask your teacher for the answers. You can also search your textbook for answers to your questions. This will help your brain to retain all of the information being taught in class.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">So, what are the things we should remember in order to get good grades?</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\"><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://zipstudy-a.akamaihd.net/images/articles/guide-to-get-good-grades-only.png\" alt=\"If you want to get good grades, pay attention to the following issues.\" width=\"650\" height=\"206\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">By going through the tips above, you can begin improving your grades in no time at all. Before you know it, you will have the grades you want and be on your way to a new grade point average.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">There is also another way to get your A - <a title=\"Place an Order\" href=\"https://www.ozessay.com.au/order\">become our customer</a>! Our team of professional writers and 24/7 support can\'t wait to help you!&nbsp;</p>','How to Get Good Grades at College? OZessay Knows the Correct Answer!','','publish','closed','closed','','how-to-get-good-grades','','','2017-05-16 14:32:43','2017-05-16 11:32:43','',0,'',0,'page','',0),(252,1,'2012-03-20 19:15:13','2012-03-20 17:15:13','','how-to-get-good-grades-in-college-oz-v3','','inherit','closed','closed','','how-to-get-good-grades-in-college-oz-v3','','','2017-05-16 14:32:43','2017-05-16 11:32:43','',251,'https://ozessay-a.akamaihd.net/content/3/en/images/articles/how-to-get-good-grades-in-college-oz-v3.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpg',0),(253,1,'2016-12-29 12:01:18','2016-12-29 10:01:18','<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">A&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.ozessay.com.au/persuasive-essay-writing-service\">persuasive essay</a>&nbsp;is an essay that uses reason along with logic so the person reading it can see that one idea is more justifiable than another idea. The purpose of a persuasive essay is to influence the reader to take on a particular viewpoint or to adopt a certain action. It is imperative that the persuasive essay has solid evidence within it and sound reasoning. &nbsp;</p>\r\n<hr />\r\n<h4 style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><a href=\"https://www.ozessay.com.au/how-to-write-a-persuasive-essay\">HOW TO WRITE A PERSUASIVE ESSAY</a></strong></h4>\r\n<hr />\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">To write a persuasive essay is not a big deal&nbsp;since a persuasive essay outline is simple to follow: introduction, body paragraphs, and conclusion.</p>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">10 Persuasive Essay Topics on History</h2>\r\n<p><em>1. The Spanish Inquisition was a hurdle to the scientific progress.&nbsp;</em></p>\r\n<p><em>2. Western museums should repatriate artifacts to the countries of their origin.&nbsp;</em></p>\r\n<p><em>3. Slavery in the global economic development. &nbsp;</em></p>\r\n<p><em>4. Pearl Harbor attack changed the flow of history.&nbsp;</em></p>\r\n<p><em>5. The day that changed America: 9/11.&nbsp;</em></p>\r\n<p><em>6. The bombings of Hiroshima and Nagasaki can\'t be justified.&nbsp;</em></p>\r\n<p><em>7. Holocaust denial is an attempt of historical revisionism.&nbsp;</em></p>\r\n<p><em>8. The Cold War and arms race of 1947-1991 stimulated the scientific progress in the confronting countries.&nbsp;</em></p>\r\n<p><em>9. The Trail of Tears was the greatest crime against the indigenous population.&nbsp;</em></p>\r\n<p><em>10. Hitler was central to the development of the Nazism ideology.&nbsp;</em></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">If you need more persuasive essay topics here is a great list of the most popular topics of 2017.</p>\r\n<hr />\r\n<h4 style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><a href=\"https://www.ozessay.com.au/persuasive-writing-topics\">BEST PERSUASIVE WRITING TOPICS IN 2017</a></strong>&nbsp;</h4>\r\n<hr />\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">No time to focus on writing a persuasive essay? <a href=\"https://www.ozessay.com.au/order\">Place an order</a> and our professionals will write a great paper for you.</p>','Persuasive Writing Topics: Look Deep into History with OZessay','','publish','closed','closed','','10-persuasive-essay-topics-history','','','2017-05-16 16:42:44','2017-05-16 13:42:44','',0,'',0,'page','',0),(254,1,'2016-12-29 12:01:18','2016-12-29 10:01:18','','persuasive-essay-topics10-7-v4','','inherit','closed','closed','','persuasive-essay-topics10-7-v4','','','2017-05-16 16:42:44','2017-05-16 13:42:44','',253,'https://ozessay-a.akamaihd.net/content/3/en/images/articles/persuasive-essay-topics10-7-v4.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpg',0),(255,1,'2014-01-31 09:17:32','2014-01-31 07:17:32','<p style=\"text-align: left;\">Writing essays is certainly an important component in the academic curriculums of any educational establishment. Essay assignments account for over 40% of the subject marks in most course modules, which makes essay writing one of the essential academic skills. Developing such skills is not as easy as it seems and this task remains difficult for many students even in their senior years. This is why many students resort to the assistance of essay writing companies who specialize in writing high-scoring essays. Papers that are produced by professional essay writing companies are to be used as sample essays that teach how to write essays effectively. Therefore, if you too are facing difficulties in writing a high-quality essay, get help from a high caliber essay writing company and sharpen your writing skills.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">If you are finding it hard to cope with your essay writing assignments, do not keep putting off the assignment until the last day before the deadline. Instead, <strong><a style=\"text-decoration: none;\" title=\"Writing Help\" href=\"https://www.ozessay.com.au/order\">select a good essay writing service</a></strong> to help you with the assignment.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: left;\">Selecting the Right Writing Service</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">The competition within the writing assistance industry is extremely tough, and substandard companies leave the market quickly. Yet, you should be careful when selecting a writing service to work on your project &ndash; remember to choose the service that has experience, credibility and is capable of addressing your needs effectively.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">If you seek help from a fraudulent or substandard company, you are bound to end up in bigger trouble than if you would attempt to complete the essay assignment on your own. Therefore, make sure to extend due diligence when it comes to selecting the right party for writing your custom essay. It is a better strategy to invest time in the selection of a proper company rather than trying to resolve problems that start emerging at the order completion stage. When searching for a professional essay writer, select a well-established firm, with a large pool of writers as opposed to depending on a single essay writer. This reduces the risk of depending on a single writer who may become unavailable at any point. A company with a large pool of writing professionals can easily switch your order to an equally competent writer immediately, allowing you to still meet the deadlines.</p>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: left;\">Selection Considerations to Bear in Mind</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">If you are a student who is searching for a good writing assistance service, here are some key points to consider. Paying attention to these points at the screening phase will help you locate a trustworthy writing service with good essay writers.</p>\r\n<ul style=\"text-align: left;\">\r\n<li><strong>Website</strong> &ndash; Check the website appearance, quality, functionality and the user friendliness of the writing company. If their web content is written shoddily, the chances of your assignment getting written in a professional manner are quite slim. The site should also facilitate communication between writer, you and staff. The option for uploading files and researched text material should be available as well.</li>\r\n<li><strong>Writers</strong> &ndash; By going through the writer profiles, you can get a fairly good idea of their level and the quality of their writing. Most high-quality writing services engage competent writers with Ph.D. and Masters level qualifications in various subject areas, plus years of experience in the essay and various other academic paper writing.</li>\r\n<li><strong>Customer Service</strong> &ndash; Contact the website via phone or instant messaging systems and assess their level of professionalism and helpfulness in answering your questions as well as their willingness to assist. The level of professionalism of the front desk staff will certainly be a reflection of the quality of service you can expect once you place your essay order.</li>\r\n<li><strong>Price</strong> &ndash; Price is generally the first thing which students would consider, mainly as cash is not in abundance in students&rsquo; wallets. However, we advise you not to choose the cheapest, as you may just end up with a substandard quality essay. It is better to select a writing service which charges industry averages or even slightly more. After all, high-quality writers with Ph.D. or Masters Degrees are highly unlikely to work for very low rates.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\"><strong><a style=\"text-decoration: none;\" title=\"Writing Help\" href=\"https://www.ozessay.com.au/order\">Request for a custom wrote essay</a></strong> sample that is tailored to all the requirements of your assignment. This will help you learn how to answer your essay question, in the same manner, a professional writer with subject expertise would do. With essay writing assistance, your essay will surely get you an excellent grade. What&rsquo;s more, you will sharpen your writing skills by analyzing professionally written essays completed by the writing professionals.&nbsp;</p>','What You Need to Consider Before Choosing A Writing Service','','publish','closed','closed','','essay-writing-assistance','','','2017-05-17 11:46:33','2017-05-17 08:46:33','',0,'',0,'page','',0),(256,1,'2014-01-31 09:17:32','2014-01-31 07:17:32','','what_to_consider_before_choosing_a_writing_service_ozessay','','inherit','closed','closed','','what_to_consider_before_choosing_a_writing_service_ozessay','','','2017-05-17 11:46:33','2017-05-17 08:46:33','',255,'https://ozessay-a.akamaihd.net/images/article/og/what_to_consider_before_choosing_a_writing_service_ozessay.jpg?v=1495616418',0,'attachment','image/jpg',0),(257,1,'2013-10-25 11:53:42','2013-10-25 08:53:42','<blockquote> <q>Dissertation writing help you may get online from OZessay.</q> </blockquote><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Dissertation writing generally comes as the final requirement of a degree program. Unless this requirement is fulfilled successfully, you will not get the degree you have worked hard for. This is not a task that can be done in a few days, nor can it be completed in ad-hoc fashion. Writing a dissertation calls for proper planning and sticking to the planned timeframes for each phase of the dissertation project. Dissertation projects require planning, effort, knowledge and dedication. Students pursuing graduate to doctoral degrees need to submit a successful dissertation that will pass the scrutiny of the dissertation panel. Some dissertations pass on their first submission while others may be returned for minor modifications or for resubmissions with major changes. Dissertations that totally deviate from the requirements, or found to be plagiarized will be rejected or failed by the dissertation committee.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">Therefore, all students have a clear understanding of the importance of submitting a well-written dissertation, in order to complete their degree successfully. Yet, despite realizing the importance of submitting a high-quality dissertation, very few students are able to manage this task on their own to a satisfactory level. Hence, many choose to secure dissertation help from a professional dissertation writing service. Exclusive, top quality research papers developed from in-depth research and tailored to your requirements is what you get when you <a style=\"text-decoration: none;\" title=\"Place an Order\" href=\"https://www.ozessay.com.au/order\">place your order</a> with <em>OZessay.com.au.</em>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: left;\">Dissertation Help Can Be Varied</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">A dissertation has different components that have to come together to create an outstanding work of academic brilliance. The entire project involves formulating a good dissertation question, conducting rigorous research, reviewing literature, analyzing data and the actual dissertation writing. Students can get dissertation help to handle either one of these components&nbsp;or the whole dissertation. For instance, if you are unable to come up with a good dissertation proposal, you could enlist a professional writer to formulate a good proposal with an interesting and unique hypothesis or question. This will ensure the approval from the dissertation committee to initiate and proceed with the actual study without any delays. The design of a robust methodology, conducting rigorous field research, data analysis and the writing of the actual dissertation are the other aspects for which can enlist dissertation help. For those struggling to grasp the formal writing styles, a professional dissertation writer can be of major help. Besides assisting with academic writing, a dissertation writing service can assist with statistical analysis. A well-established dissertation writing service will provide writers who are able to handle various data analysis software such as SPSS and Minitab, which are commonly used in the dissertation research projects.</p>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: left;\">How Can Professional Writing Service Help?</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">There are many types of dissertation help, which can be obtained from a writing service.&nbsp; Students can first and foremost read on various pieces of advice, and go through the free dissertation tips available online. They can also enlist a dissertation writer for writing an outstanding dissertation proposal. Once a writer is chosen, you can request to write either the entire dissertation or its selected chapters. In addition, if you are writing a dissertation yourself, but are not so sure about the purity of your style, you can request dissertation editing. Since dissertations need to comply with strict formatting rules, students can pass on this important task to a dissertation editor who is well versed with formatting and style guides such as the APA or Harvard style.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">While it is indeed a major relief to have a professional writing service to provide dissertation help, securing such services should be done carefully. Due to the virtual nature of the writing services, fraudulent operators can set up websites to scam students of their money. There can also be sites that claim to be professional but lack the resources and qualified writers to deliver quality work. Therefore, when selecting a writing service for your dissertation help, make sure to select a high caliber, well established one with due diligence at the screening phase. When you are allocated a professional dissertation writer, your project can benefit from his or her experience in dissertation writing. Most of these writers have written a number of successful dissertations and know the procedure, style as well as the possible pitfalls. Collaborate closely with the writer and be involved completely, even if you have requested for a <a style=\"text-decoration: none;\" href=\"../../custom-dissertation\">custom written dissertation</a>. This can ensure that year of effort put in to the degree program is not wasted at this final stage.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-decoration: none; text-align: center;\"><strong><a style=\"text-decoration: none;\" title=\"Place an Order\" href=\"https://www.ozessay.com.au/order\">CLICK HERE TO ORDER YOUR CUSTOM WRITTEN DISSERTATION!</a></strong>&nbsp;</p>','Dissertation Help: Pro Help to Ensure a Place in the Graduation','','publish','closed','closed