 Woman\'s place is at work.&nbsp;</em></p>\r\n<p><em>4. Men need protection from feminists\' attacks.&nbsp;</em></p>\r\n<p><em>5. Men should open doors to women.&nbsp;</em></p>\r\n<p><em>6. Women should retain their birth names after marriage.&nbsp;</em></p>\r\n<p><em>7. Research on male pregnancy should not be encouraged.&nbsp;</em></p>\r\n<p><em>8. Women in combat weaken armed forces.&nbsp;</em></p>\r\n<p><em>9. It is OK for men to cry.&nbsp;</em></p>\r\n<p><em>10. Gender roles </em>aren\'t gender<em> requirements.</em></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">If you need more persuasive essay topics here is a great list of the most popular topics of 2017.</p>\r\n<hr />\r\n<h4 style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><a href=\"https://www.ozessay.com.au/persuasive-writing-topics\">BEST PERSUASIVE WRITING TOPICS IN 2017</a></strong></h4>\r\n<hr />\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">No time to focus on writing your own persuasive&nbsp;essay? We can write one for you! Feel free to <a href=\"https://www.ozessay.com.au/order\">place an&nbsp;order</a> for a custom-written persuasive&nbsp;essay&nbsp;at very reasonable rates.</p>','10 Persuasive Writing Topics: Gender Roles','','publish','closed','closed','','10-persuasive-essay-topics-gender-roles','','','2017-05-17 12:52:04','2017-05-17 09:52:04','',0,'',0,'page','',0),(466,1,'2016-11-19 20:45:24','2016-11-19 18:45:24','','persuasive_essay_topics_gender_roles_ozessay','','inherit','closed','closed','','persuasive_essay_topics_gender_roles_ozessay','','','2017-05-17 12:52:04','2017-05-17 09:52:04','',465,'https://ozessay-a.akamaihd.net/images/article/og/persuasive_essay_topics_gender_roles_ozessay.jpg?v=1495699004',0,'attachment','image/jpg',0),(467,1,'2016-11-19 21:25:06','2016-11-19 19:25:06','<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">A&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.ozessay.com.au/persuasive-essay-writing-service\">persuasive essay</a>&nbsp;is an essay that uses reason along with logic so the person reading it can see that one idea is more justifiable than another idea. The purpose of a persuasive essay is to influence the reader to take on a particular viewpoint or to adopt a certain action. It is imperative that the persuasive essay has solid evidence within it and sound reasoning. &nbsp;</p>\r\n<hr />\r\n<h4 style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><a href=\"https://www.ozessay.com.au/how-to-write-a-persuasive-essay\">HOW TO WRITE A PERSUASIVE ESSAY</a></strong></h4>\r\n<hr />\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">To write a persuasive essay is not a big deal&nbsp;since a persuasive essay outline is simple to follow: introduction, body paragraphs, and conclusion.</p>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">10 Persuasive Essay Topics on Ethical Dilemmas</h2>\r\n<p><em>1. Surrogacy should be legalized.</em></p>\r\n<p><em>2. All countries should abandon nuclear weapon.</em></p>\r\n<p><em>3. Companies using animal testing should pay higher taxes.&nbsp;</em></p>\r\n<p><em>4. Only victims of accidents can use plastic surgery.&nbsp;</em></p>\r\n<p><em>5. Professional actors shouldn\'t be allowed to play poker.&nbsp;</em></p>\r\n<p><em>6. Leather and fur clothes should be outlawed.&nbsp;</em></p>\r\n<p><em>7. Teens should have access to birth control pills.&nbsp;</em></p>\r\n<p><em>8. Politics and church should be separate.&nbsp;</em></p>\r\n<p><em>9. News writers should never distort the truth to astonish audiences.&nbsp;<strong><br /></strong></em></p>\r\n<p><em>10. Should teens have plastic surgery?</em></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">If you need more persuasive essay topics here is a great list of the most popular topics of 2017.</p>\r\n<hr />\r\n<h4 style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><a href=\"https://www.ozessay.com.au/persuasive-writing-topics\">BEST PERSUASIVE WRITING TOPICS IN 2017</a></strong>&nbsp;</h4>\r\n<hr />\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">No time to think&nbsp;of these ethical dilemmas when writing your own persuasive&nbsp;essay? We can write one for you! Feel free to 